column78: What is the importance/urgency to XML Amsterdam 2012 attendees of XML-related training? (1) - static web sites, (2) - interacting with static online video, (3) - interacting with an instructor online, (4) - interacting with an instructor at a public-subscribed event, (5) - interacting with an instructor at an on-client-site event    What are the important/urgent topics for XML-related training? (1) - XML syntax, (2) - XPath data model and syntax, (3) - Schema languages, (4) - XSLT, (5) - XSL-FO, (6) - XML 'Semantics', (7) - XML vocabularies    Good luck at the conference!  . . . . . . . .  Ken
